The Travelers Corp's TravelersMortgage Services said it signed a letter of intent to buy twosubsidiaries of the privately-held &lt;Equitable Life AssuranceSociety of the U.S.>    The company said it plans to acquire the EquitableRelocation Management Corp and the Equitable Realty NetworkInc.    The company said the acquisitions will give it broaderdistribution of its corporate relocation service and mortgageprograms. Reuter&#3;